1202
01:12:41,315 --> 01:12:42,316
(ISABELLA SCREAMING)

1203
01:12:42,400 --> 01:12:44,073
Michael, put the camera down!

1204
01:12:48,739 --> 01:12:52,334
Listen to me. I'm a priest.
Please, go and help those people.

1205
01:12:52,410 --> 01:12:54,583
- Keep her here.
- DOCTOR: Thank you, Father.

1206
01:12:55,746 --> 01:12:58,420
Okay, let's go, let's go, let's go.

1207
01:13:01,252 --> 01:13:02,879
- Come on.
- MICHAEL: She just killed that woman.

1208
01:13:03,254 --> 01:13:04,972
BEN: We need to end this.

1209
01:13:05,673 --> 01:13:09,348
Grab her legs. Help me grab her legs!
We're going to Father Gallo's.

1210
01:13:09,594 --> 01:13:10,766
MICHAEL: What's he going to do?

1211
01:13:10,928 --> 01:13:13,522
BEN: I need help with the exorcism.

1212
01:13:14,599 --> 01:13:16,442
Get the door. Get the door.

1213
01:13:16,851 --> 01:13:18,023
BEN: Oh, my God. What have I done?

1214
01:13:18,185 --> 01:13:19,778
You really think Gallo's going to help?

1215
01:13:20,021 --> 01:13:21,443
Yeah, I need help.

1216
01:13:22,023 --> 01:13:24,196
- I need to fix this.
(GASPING)

1217
01:13:24,275 --> 01:13:26,198
Oh, shit. Oh, shit. She's waking up.

1218
01:13:26,527 --> 01:13:28,029
She's waking up.

1219
01:13:28,613 --> 01:13:31,287
We haven't got much time, Michael.
We haven't got much time.

1220
01:13:31,616 --> 01:13:33,710
Stay with me. Don't let it get to you.

1221
01:13:34,952 --> 01:13:38,456
When I was 13,
my uncle told me he was an exorcist.

1222
01:13:39,457 --> 01:13:42,006
You can't get back
into God's good graces, priest.

1223
01:13:42,084 --> 01:13:43,711
(WHISPERING) Not after what you did.

1224
01:13:44,420 --> 01:13:45,467
Ben?

1225
01:13:45,713 --> 01:13:47,511
(DISTORTED) You wanted him to die,
didn't you?

1226
01:13:48,007 --> 01:13:49,179
What is she doing?

1227
01:13:49,508 --> 01:13:51,806
(IN MALE VOICE)
He says to say, "Thank you."

1228
01:13:52,303 --> 01:13:53,805
Who are you?

1229
01:13:54,305 --> 01:13:57,309
You know me. Everyone knows me.

1230
01:13:57,642 --> 01:14:00,065
- Lord, have mercy! Christ, have mercy!
(SCREAMING)

1231
01:14:00,144 --> 01:14:01,270
Jesus.

1232
01:14:01,354 --> 01:14:02,480
God the Father!

1233
01:14:03,105 --> 01:14:04,322
(SCREECHING)

1234
01:14:04,398 --> 01:14:05,399
Oh, my God!

1235
01:14:06,817 --> 01:14:07,818
Oh, shit!

1236
01:14:07,902 --> 01:14:09,279
(SCREAMING)
(TIRES SCREECHING)

1237
01:14:09,654 --> 01:14:12,032
BEN: Your place is in solitude!

1238
01:14:12,531 --> 01:14:15,159
Your abode is in the nest of serpents!

1239
01:14:15,242 --> 01:14:17,370
Be gone forthwith
from this servant of God!

1240
01:14:17,745 --> 01:14:20,214
Get out of her! Get out of her!

1241
01:14:20,289 --> 01:14:22,542
(BEN RECITING PRAYERS IN LATIN)

1242
01:14:28,047 --> 01:14:29,390
It's working, right?

1243
01:14:29,632 --> 01:14:31,634
I have got her under control,
but I don't know for how long.

1244
01:14:31,717 --> 01:14:33,060
You've got to hurry up.

1245
01:14:37,932 --> 01:14:38,933
(PANTING) It's okay.

1246
01:14:40,351 --> 01:14:42,479
It's going to be okay. I'm sorry.

1247
01:14:42,561 --> 01:14:43,608
(ALARM BLEEPING)

1248
01:14:43,688 --> 01:14:45,281
Just be strong.

1249
01:14:45,856 --> 01:14:47,199
- Be strong.
(ENGINE REWING)

1250
01:14:48,693 --> 01:14:49,990
Just be strong.

1251
01:14:50,069 --> 01:14:51,036
(VEHICLE HONKING)

1252
01:14:51,112 --> 01:14:52,204
Michael!

1253
01:14:54,573 --> 01:14:56,075
(CRASHING)